282 struct EstimationControl
283 {
284  struct EnableFlags : Bitfield<EnableFlags>
285  {
286  enum _enumType : uint16_t
287  {
288  NONE = 0x0000,
289  GYRO_BIAS = 0x0001,
290  ACCEL_BIAS = 0x0002,
291  GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0004,
292  ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0008,
293  ANTENNA_OFFSET = 0x0010,
294  AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON = 0x0020,
295  AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON = 0x0040,
296  ALL = 0x007F,
297  };
298  uint16_t value = NONE;
299 
300  EnableFlags() : value(NONE) {}
301  EnableFlags(int val) : value((uint16_t)val) {}
302  operator uint16_t() const { return value; }
303  EnableFlags& operator=(uint16_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
304  EnableFlags& operator=(int val) { value = val; return *this; }
305  EnableFlags& operator|=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
306  EnableFlags& operator&=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
307 
308  bool gyroBias() const { return (value & GYRO_BIAS) > 0; }
309  void gyroBias(bool val) { if(val) value |= GYRO_BIAS; else value &= ~GYRO_BIAS; }
310  bool accelBias() const { return (value & ACCEL_BIAS) > 0; }
311  void accelBias(bool val) { if(val) value |= ACCEL_BIAS; else value &= ~ACCEL_BIAS; }
312  bool gyroScaleFactor() const { return (value & GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
313  void gyroScaleFactor(bool val) { if(val) value |= GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; else value &= ~GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; }
314  bool accelScaleFactor() const { return (value & ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
315  void accelScaleFactor(bool val) { if(val) value |= ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; else value &= ~ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; }
316  bool antennaOffset() const { return (value & ANTENNA_OFFSET) > 0; }
317  void antennaOffset(bool val) { if(val) value |= ANTENNA_OFFSET; else value &= ~ANTENNA_OFFSET; }
318  bool autoMagHardIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON) > 0; }
319  void autoMagHardIron(bool val) { if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; else value &= ~AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; }
320  bool autoMagSoftIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON) > 0; }
321  void autoMagSoftIron(bool val) { if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; else value &= ~AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; }
322 
323  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
324  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
325  };

3303 struct InitializationConfiguration
3304 {
3305  struct AlignmentSelector : Bitfield<AlignmentSelector>
3306  {
3307  enum _enumType : uint8_t
3308  {
3309  NONE = 0x00,
3310  DUAL_ANTENNA = 0x01,
3311  KINEMATIC = 0x02,
3312  MAGNETOMETER = 0x04,
3313  EXTERNAL = 0x08,
3314  ALL = 0x0F,
3315  };
3316  uint8_t value = NONE;
3317 
3318  AlignmentSelector() : value(NONE) {}
3319  AlignmentSelector(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
3320  operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
3321  AlignmentSelector& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
3322  AlignmentSelector& operator=(int val) { value = val; return *this; }
3323  AlignmentSelector& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
3324  AlignmentSelector& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
3325 
3326  bool dualAntenna() const { return (value & DUAL_ANTENNA) > 0; }
3327  void dualAntenna(bool val) { if(val) value |= DUAL_ANTENNA; else value &= ~DUAL_ANTENNA; }
3328  bool kinematic() const { return (value & KINEMATIC) > 0; }
3329  void kinematic(bool val) { if(val) value |= KINEMATIC; else value &= ~KINEMATIC; }
3330  bool magnetometer() const { return (value & MAGNETOMETER) > 0; }
3331  void magnetometer(bool val) { if(val) value |= MAGNETOMETER; else value &= ~MAGNETOMETER; }
3332  bool external() const { return (value & EXTERNAL) > 0; }
3333  void external(bool val) { if(val) value |= EXTERNAL; else value &= ~EXTERNAL; }
3334 
3335  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
3336  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
3337  };
